  "body": "To keep scale of color-coding consistent during multiple explanations on the same image.\r\n\r\nFor example, I have been working on an app where you compute explanation for the same image at different times during training, to see how feature importance changes during training (in a particular setting where this make sense: Continual Learning. I am visualizing catastrophic forgetting) But if scale of the color-coding changes at every plot, the sequence of explanation doen't make sense anymore (visually)",
